.za 1.5
.ue 1
                                                                       $.#$
                                                         Calw 5th August 66
My dear Frederic

.ue 2
                                                                       $.#$
Forts.: 5th August 66
I am going to send you your box very soon, in it you will send a few things
for David. also I trust a piece of heidebeer Cake which you shall part for
your three gentlemen and David. I intend D.V. to have wash the week papa is
to go to Stutgart for the Mission feast. I will still write you afterward
about it. How is Nast? have you some work? is there prospect that it will
soon be better? I am very glad that your dog has been found, it is a good
sighn for unkel! Do you hear any thing of Charles Weigle, is he to come to
Stutgart?

I hope you are happy in the Lord and well in your body!

With love to you all
.fo -
                              Yours affectly
                                      J. Gundert

Please buy for me 100 Corcks <corks>* "pfrofen" large ones those I buy here
are very small. they have none bigger here
.ns
.dr HG060866
